This code is to create a page to view gallery in form of Galleriffic (1 big photo and 1 block of thumbnails).
Require: Views Galleriffic module.

Code: page_own-photos.txt

Note: This configuration need the patched Views Galleriffic. Please see the patch in ../../mbm_modules folder.

Image Style for big photo: Scale 500x500 (Large).

The Photo Map block is to show photo's location on the map.
